text: Anna Júlia Csiki (born 14 November 1999) is a Hungarian footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Hungary women's national team. ==Career== Anna Csiki has been capped for the Hungary national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian women's footballers Category:Hungary women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:Kopparbergs/Göteborg FC players Category:Ferencvárosi TC (women) footballers
